n="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/890359e4-d4bd-44dc-999a-c417f34eb027.png" style="width: 22px;height: 20px;margin: 0px;border: 0;line-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="22">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/f3287432-f4f9-4f0a-8fa1-89813f0c78d3.png" style="width: 18px;height: 20px;margin: 0px;border: 0;line-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="18"><br>\r\nGiven a grid of size m x n, calculate the total number of rectangles contained in this rectangle. All integer sizes and positions are counted.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=de7ecb7c4f&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;">pj6444</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style="font-size:16px"><span style="line-height:20.7999992370605px"><img align="none" height="26" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/6_kyu.png" style="width: 50px;height: 26px;margin: 0px;border: 0;line-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="50">&nbsp; <a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=eb29c9b7cb&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;">RNA to Protein Sequence Translation&nbsp; &nbsp;</a></span></span><img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/prog_js02_red_01.1.png" style="opacity: 0.9;font-family: tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;font-size: 17.7777786254883px;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: -3px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;height: auto !important;" width="20">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="17" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/prog_ruby_red_01.png" style="width: 17px;height: 17px;margin: 0px;border: 0;line-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="17">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/097215bc-68e2-44b2-a9b4-15fddb6b3b06.png" style="opacity: 0.9;font-family: tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;font-size: 17.7777786254883px;line-height: 1.6em;width: 20px;height: 20px;margin: 0px 0px -3px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="20">&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\r\nGiven a string of RNA, create a funciton which translates the RNA into its protein sequence. Note: the test cases will always produce a valid string. &nbsp;<a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=d6b9809a7d&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;torret</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style="line-height:20.7999992370605px"><img align="none" height="26" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/5_kyu.png" style="width: 50px;height: 26px;margin: 0px;border: 0;line-height: 100%;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="50">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:16px"><a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage2.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=8da99a92f9&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;">Josephus Permutation</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span><img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/prog_js02_red_01.1.png" style="opacity: 0.9;font-family: tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;font-size: 17.7777786254883px;line-height: 1.6em;width: 20px;height: 20px;margin: 0px 0px -3px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="20">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="17" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/prog_ruby_red_01.png" style="opacity: 0.9;line-height: 20.7999992370605px;width: 17px;height: 17px;margin: 0px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="17">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/097215bc-68e2-44b2-a9b4-15fddb6b3b06.png" style="opacity: 0.9;font-family: tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;font-size: 17.7777786254883px;line-height: 1.6em;width: 20px;height: 20px;margin: 0px 0px -3px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="20"><br>\r\nYou are to create a function that returns a Josephus permutation, taking as parameters the initial array/list of items to be permuted as if they were in a circle and counted out every k places until none remained.&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=ffcfd81066&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;">GiacomoSorbi</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img align="none" height="26" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/4_kyu.png" style="opacity: 0.9;line-height: 20.7999992370605px;width: 50px;height: 26px;margin: 0px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;" width="50">&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://codewars.us5.list-manage.com/track/click?u=13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0&id=bbc28f4e04&e=03671ad129" target="_blank" style="color: #cb3d2b;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:16px">Simple Memory Manager</span></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img align="none" height="20" src="https://gallery.mailchimp.com/13bbf05035a7fd3e5b7abcdf0/images/prog_js02_red_01.1.png" style="opacity: 0.9;font-family: tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;font-size: 17.7777786254883px;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: -3px;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;height: auto !important;" width="20">&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>\r\nOne of the service